snippet.title: PlayStation - Hikari no Shima - Seven Lithographs in Shining Island (1999) - Intro
snippet.description:
DESCRIPTION
Hikari no Shima: Seven Lithographs in Shining Island is an Action game, developed and published by Affect, which was released in Japan in 1999.
